{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"53491-ek-trana-panch-madad-madad","title":"એક, ત્રણ, પાંચ — મદદ, મદદ!","description":"નારિયેળીના ઝાડમાં વસતા એક ભમરાને ગણતરી કરવી બહુ ગમે. ઠેકઠેકાણે એ એકી અને બેકી સંખ્યાઓની શોધમાં રહે. એક દિવસ એ ઊંધો પડી જાય છે. તો ચાલો, જોઈએ કે તેની મદદમાં કેટલા મિત્રો આવે છે? એકી સંખ્યામાં આવે છે કે બેકી સંખ્યામાં આવે છે?","language":"Gujarati","langCode":"gu","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Parth Trivedi"],"illustrators":["Sonal Gupta Vaswani"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/53491-ek-trana-panch-madad-madad"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/725492/size3/3ecd3874b39dcc8551a41c3b387e60ab.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/725492/size6/3ecd3874b39dcc8551a41c3b387e60ab.jpg"},"audio":{"src":"https://storage.googleapis.com/story-weaver-e2e-production/stories/53491/audios/story/53491-ek-trana-panch-madad-madad.mp3","cues":[[1,0,2.04],[2,2.04,3.08],[3,3.08,3.84],[4,3.84,4.32],[5,4.32,4.64],[6,4.64,5.4],[7,5.4,6.24],[8,6.24,6.4],[9,6.4,6.8],[10,6.8,7.4],[11,7.4,7.8],[12,7.8,8.2],[13,8.2,8.74],[14,8.74,9.1],[15,9.1,9.76],[16,9.76,11],[17,11,11.14],[18,11.14,11.4],[19,11.4,13],[20,13,14.64],[21,14.64,16.04],[22,16.04,17.04],[23,17.04,17.48],[24,17.48,17.88],[25,17.88,18.24],[26,18.24,18.24],[27,18.24,19.3],[28,19.3,19.92],[29,19.92,20.6],[30,20.6,21],[31,21,21.48],[32,21.48,21.78],[33,21.78,22],[34,22,22.74],[35,22.74,24.76],[36,24.76,25.22],[37,25.22,25.6],[38,25.6,26.5],[39,26.5,26.98],[40,26.98,27.3],[41,27.3,27.72],[42,27.72,28.04],[43,28.04,28.62],[44,28.62,29.84],[45,29.84,30.46],[46,30.46,31.22],[47,31.22,31.54],[48,31.54,32.06],[49,32.06,32.34],[50,32.34,33.46],[51,33.46,33.72],[52,33.72,34